Articles.Content:
I am running a modded install including Kethane, and the map overlay is not showing properly.  Every tile on the map is purple, and I cannot see the positions of ores without hovering my pointer over them, which is very frustrating.  Is this supposed to be happening?

Screenshot: https://db.tt/5hU46gO66K

KSP.log: https://db.tt/F7rkgZJPeH
